ZH: 我们需要保持中立，以便公正地评估这项问题。
EN: We need to remain neutral in order to assess this issue fairly.

ZH: 这个仲裁员必须保持中立，不能偏袒任何一方。
EN: This arbitrator must remain neutral and not favor either party.

ZH: 那个新闻记者要在报道中保持中立，不带个人偏见。
EN: The journalist must maintain neutrality in the news report, without any personal bias.

ZH: 作为学生会主席，我必须中立地处理学生的冲突。
EN: As the president of the student council, I must handle student conflicts in a neutral manner.

ZH: 这场争议引起了很多争议，我尽量保持中立来避免偏见。
EN: This controversy has sparked a lot of debate, and I try to remain neutral to avoid bias.

ZH: 他是一个很中立的法官，从不被个人感情影响判决。
EN: He is a very neutral judge, never letting personal emotions influence his judgments.

ZH: 战争无法使人保持中立，人们总是会被迫站队。
EN: War does not allow people to remain neutral; they are always forced to take sides.

ZH: 这个选民群体在选举中通常都保持中立，很难预测他们的投票结果。
EN: This group of voters usually remains neutral in elections, making it difficult to predict their voting outcome.

ZH: 为了达到客观和中立，这个研究采用了双盲实验设计。
EN: To achieve objectivity and neutrality, this study employed a double-blind experimental design.

ZH: 媒体应该在报道中保持中立，提供客观的信息给观众。
EN: The media should maintain neutrality and provide objective information to the audience.

ZH: 中立不代表没有立场，而是要求公正和平等对待。
EN: Neutrality does not mean having no position; it demands fairness and equal treatment.

ZH: 这位裁判一直以来都受到了人们的称赞，因为他总是能保持中立。
EN: This referee has always received praise because he can always remain neutral.

ZH: 在跨国冲突中，维持中立对于和平解决非常重要。
EN: Maintaining neutrality is crucial for peaceful resolutions in international conflicts.

ZH: 这个调查机构必须保持中立，不能受到政治干预。
EN: This investigative agency must remain neutral and not be influenced by political interference.

ZH: 学术研究应该与个人信仰中立，以保证科学的真实性。
EN: Academic research should be neutral in relation to personal beliefs to ensure the scientific authenticity.

ZH: 在争议性话题上，公立电视台应该保持中立，不偏袒任何一方。
EN: Public television stations should remain neutral and not favor any side on controversial topics.

ZH: 请你在争论中保持中立，不要过于偏向你自己的观点。
EN: Please remain neutral in the argument and do not lean too heavily towards your own standpoint.

ZH: 在辩论中，我们必须尊重对方的观点，并试着保持中立。
EN: In a debate, we must respect the opposing views and try to remain neutral.

ZH: 他的观点很中立，能够从不同角度看问题。
EN: His opinions are very neutral, and he can see issues from different perspectives.

ZH: 不偏不倚地保持中立是一个好的领导者应具备的能力。
EN: The ability to remain neutral without bias is a quality that a good leader should possess.
